TAKE ON THE WORLD with the American Tourister Prismo! Available @ http://www.bagworld.com.au/shop/brands/american-tourister-prismo-luggage-suitcases-bags/
Travel...new places, familiar faces, and endless possibilities. American Tourister is ready to go when you are, ensuring your travels are met with confidence. American Tourister knows how you travel, that's why it's the smart choice with luggage that's right for you.
The American Tourister Prismo is beautifully designed, with clean and sleek curves defining its silhouette. Its pearlised gloss finish composes a subtle two-tone stripe pattern on its surface. The Prismo collection is available in a sizzling palette of five exuberant summer colours and also charcoal for the monochrome lovers. Made of Polycarbonate (PC), and the range features a lightweight construction, yet is strong and sturdy with maximum durability and security.
Main features of the American Tourister Prismo Hardside Suitcase include:
-360 degree multidirectional spinner wheels -Fully lined interior with cross ribbons that make packing easier -Inbuilt TSA approved combination lock -Lightweight design

video:video.video:title: Lock N Roll
video:video.video:description:
Get ready to Lock ‘n’ Roll to your destination with American Tourister's latest hard suitcase. Enjoy maximum packing space and a great, dynamic design, 100% made in Europe.
Lock ‘n’ Roll does exactly what it says it should: Super secure thanks to the integrated 3 point lock with TSA function, and super smooth rolling comfort thanks to 4 double wheels. Alongside great interior organisation with cross ribbons and a practical monotube wheel handle, you have a choice super vibrant colour combinations!
